1  E ndalo Merodak-baladan wuod Baladan, ma ruodh Babulon, nooro joote ir Hezekia gi barupe kod mich, nikech ne owinjo ni yande otuo, to koro osedoko mangima. 
2  Hezekia norwako jootego, monyisogi mwandune duto mane ni e ode mar keno, kaka fedha gi dhahabu gi gik mang’ue ng’ar, gi mo ma nengone tek kod gilweny, kaachiel gi gik moko duto mane ni kuonde kanone. Onge gimoro amora e ode kata e pinye mane ok onyisogi.


3  To bang’e janabi Isaya nobiro ir ruoth Hezekia, mopenjee niya, “Jogi oa kanye? To wach ang’o mokelogi?” Hezekia nodwoke ni, “Gia e piny Babulon, kuma bor.” 
4  Janabi Isaya nomedo penje niya, “To ang’o ma gineno e odi?” Hezekia nodwoke ni, “Giseneno gik moko duto manie oda. Onge gimoro amora modong’ mak anyisogi e kuonde kenona.” 
5  Bang’ mano Isaya nowacho ni Hezekia niya, “Winj wach Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto. 
6  Ndalo biro ma gik moko duto manie odi, ma kwereni osekano nyaka chil kawuono, noter Babulon. Bende Ruoth Nyasaye omedo wacho ni onge gima nodong’ kata achiel mak oter. 
7  

Yawuoti moko nolok wasumbini. Adier moko kuom yawuoti hie nolok wasumbni mabuoch e od ruodh Babulon.” 
8  Hezekia ne odwoke niya, “Wach Ruoth Nyasaye ma isenyisa ber.” To ne odwoke kamano, koparo ni en to kue biro siko e ndalone duto.

